'''Conflict-Yellow''' was a stage of [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] military status.

It was raised during periods when there was little chance of conflict during low-risk missions. Other stages of military status included [[Conflict-Red]] and [[Conflict-Orange]].

